                    "body": "The original issue was resolved with revision 1820, when Zend_Http_Request was moved into Zend_Controller_Request_Http, as getControllerName() proxies to getParam(), and the latter method checks in the $_GET and $_POST arrays if the parameter is not in the user params.\n\nThe secondary issue of the __get() functionality was resolved in revision 1900 (w00t! revision 1900!).",
